{"tid":263003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「國際化」人民幣全球排第「七」，風光不再","createTime":"2017-05-29T16:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T14:27:12.000Z","uid":33307,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de8a7084de95917ff3b4336d1b7d4fb14bba656f","tid":263003,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/67890-768x351.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F67890-768x351.png&h=a17ea228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家覺唔覺得，人民幣風光不再？唔只係少咗人關注，而係&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n原來，數據上人仔真係大不如前，睇Swift嘅國際交易使用追踪數據顯示，今年4月份人民幣嘅國際交易使用比率減少達1.6%，4月全球人民幣支付額按月大跌24.24%，排名跌到第7位，係2015年2月以來最差排名。<br />\n<br />\n睇排名，2015年時，人仔只係輸畀美元、歐元、英鎊同日圓，仲記得，當時有人話要港幣同美元脫勾，改掛人仔﹗但今時今日，人仔於國際嘅交易量，排名仲差過加元同瑞郎。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，自2015年風光過後，人仔嘅國際地位就一直滑落，有指係因為中國經濟放緩，打擊外資入貨興趣，亦有指呢兩年開始差係因為「去泡沫化」，套利交易減少。<br />\n<br />\n但無論如何，中國大國崛起，要人仔做全球第一大貨幣呢個夢，似乎就愈來愈遠了。"},{"pid":"ed72104173b8e93d80ecbc5ed012376417a23bc5","tid":263003,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"越做越衰"},{"pid":"1a3828b491e6bbb3890ff3d80950441d44361edf","tid":263003,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>港紙</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae719e3e62b10510679cf06b9a68e601cecbc9d0","tid":263003,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a718bc8e44ec6bcbdd62ee4c83e01907f9b051b","tid":263003,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"HKD第九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ffa25f0c26091a14caa1148e0acfb260bf40be","tid":263003,"ui